      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Jens Zeidler</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:242px;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jens.zeidler.54\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/9/9b/JensZeidler.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:JensZeidler.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Jens Zeidler <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Jens Zeidler</b>,<br />\na German computer scientist, alumnus of the <a href=\"/Chemnitz_University_of_Technology\" title=\"Chemnitz University of Technology\">Chemnitz University of Technology</a> with research interests in <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">artificial intelligence</a>, computer chess, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fuzzy_logic\">Fuzzy Logic</a> and <a href=\"/Learning\" title=\"Learning\">machine learning</a>. Currently, Jens Zeidler works at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Freie_Presse_(Saxony)\">Freie Presse</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1993_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1993 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jens_Zeidler&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1993_...\">1993 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jens_Zeidler&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1993 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Christian_Posthoff\" title=\"Christian Posthoff\">Christian Posthoff</a>, <a href=\"/Michael_Schlosser\" title=\"Michael Schlosser\">Michael Schlosser</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jens Zeidler</a> (<b>1993</b>). <i>Search vs. Knowledge? - Search and Knowledge!</i> In: Proc. 3rd KADS Meeting, Munich, March 8-9 1993, Siemens AG, Corporate Research and Development, 305-326, 1993.</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Christian_Posthoff\" title=\"Christian Posthoff\">Christian Posthoff</a>, <a href=\"/Michael_Schlosser\" title=\"Michael Schlosser\">Michael Schlosser</a>, <a href=\"/Rainer_Staudte\" title=\"Rainer Staudte\">Rainer Staudte</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jens Zeidler</a> (<b>1994</b>). <i>Transformations of Knowledge</i>. <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Chess_7\" title=\"Advances in Computer Chess 7\">Advances in Computer Chess 7</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jens Zeidler</a>, <a href=\"/Michael_Schlosser\" title=\"Michael Schlosser\">Michael Schlosser</a> (<b>1995</b>). <i>Unschärfe und Entscheidungsbäume</i> Beiträge zum Fachgruppentreffen Maschinelles Lernen der GI-Fachgruppe 1.1.3, <a href=\"/University_of_Dortmund\" title=\"University of Dortmund\">University of Dortmund</a>, 14.-16. August 1995, Forschungsbericht Nr. 580</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jens Zeidler</a>, <a href=\"/Michael_Schlosser\" title=\"Michael Schlosser\">Michael Schlosser</a> (<b>1996</b>). <i>Continuous-Valued Attributes in Fuzzy Decision Trees</i>. in: Proceedings of IPMU'96, Information Processing and Management of Uncertainty in Knowledge-Based Systems</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.andreas-ittner.de/\">Andreas Ittner</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jens Zeidler</a>, R. Rossius, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Werner_Dilger\">Werner Dilger</a>, <a href=\"/Michael_Schlosser\" title=\"Michael Schlosser\">Michael Schlosser</a> (<b>1997</b>). <i>Feature Space Partitioning by Non-Linear and Fuzzy Decision Trees</i>. IFSA'97</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jens_Zeidler&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Werner_Dilger\">Werner Dilger</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jens Zeidler</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i>Modellierung des Grammatiklernens in Fremdsprachen mit Active Learning</i> LIT'2M, 8. Leipziger Informatik-Tage, Leipzig, 2000, S. 89-92 (German) <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tu-chemnitz.de/informatik/HomePages/KI/publikationen/lit00.ps\">ps</a></li>\n<li> Johannes Steinmüller, Holger Langner, Marc Ritter, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jens Zeidler</a> (Hrsg.): <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.qucosa.de/recherche/frontdoor/?tx_slubopus4frontend%5bid%5d=urn:nbn:de:bsz:ch1-200800898\">15 Jahre Künstliche Intelligenz an der TU Chemnitz</a>.</i> Chemnitzer Informatikberichte, April 2008, CSR-08-01</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jens_Zeidler&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jens.zeidler.54\">Jens Zeidler | Facebook</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jens_Zeidler&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jens.zeidler.54\">Jens Zeidler | Facebook</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#RefDB\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Reference Database</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228180512\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.012 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.014 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 51/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 106/1000000\nPos